lead_paragraph: Arsenal must guard against complacency against dark horses FC Basel in their Champions League clash, manager Arsene Wenger said, as the Premier League side look to secure their first victory in the competition this season.

headline.print_headline: Wenger Warns Against Complacency Ahead of Basel Clash
